title: ‘The Ultimatum’ Episodes 1-4 Breakdown
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer is joined by Juliet Litman to chat about the first four episodes of Netflix’s newest hit, 'The Ultimatum: Marry or Move On.' They give their initial impressions of each couple, discuss the biggest WTF moments, and predict what will happen in the season finale.
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Juliet Litman
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
